00:03:29.980 --> 00:03:30.800
So there you have it guys.

00:03:30.900 --> 00:03:33.020
That's how to take a coconut husk
and turn it into a rope.

00:03:33.160 --> 00:03:35.540
Any length or any thickness
you want it to be.

00:03:36.100 --> 00:03:37.500
Thanks so much for joining me
for this experiment

00:03:37.600 --> 00:03:39.000
and I'll be looking for you
in the next one.

00:03:39.100 --> 00:03:40.200
Talk to you then.

